    <item>
      <title>巴尼耶出任法国总理给法国市场带来一些安慰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/french-markets-find-some-relief-in-barnier-s-appointment-as-pm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 被任命为法国总理，刺激了该国资产的走势，投资者希望政界人士现在将把注意力转向即将到来的预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/french-markets-find-some-relief-in-barnier-s-appointment-as-pm</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 12:29:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国银行因债务风险限制贷款，电动汽车销量或达不到目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/thai-ev-sales-to-miss-target-as-banks-curb-loans-on-debt-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家行业组织表示，由于泰国家庭债务徘徊在历史高位附近，银行在批准新的汽车贷款时变得更加谨慎，今年泰国的电动汽车销量将无法达到目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/thai-ev-sales-to-miss-target-as-banks-curb-loans-on-debt-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 12:27:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利因担任欧盟主席国而取消央行会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/hungary-cancels-central-bank-meeting-in-eu-presidency-blowback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利央行取消了一次高层会议，这是匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班担任备受争议的欧盟主席国所带来的最新附带损害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/hungary-cancels-central-bank-meeting-in-eu-presidency-blowback</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 12:26:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉的绿色燃料法有利于农民，而不是石油巨头巴西石油公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/lula-s-green-fuel-law-favors-farmers-over-oil-giant-petrobras</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西将出台新法规来支持农民，推动对生物燃料的更多需求，减少对国有石油巨头巴西石油公司生产的化石燃料的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/lula-s-green-fuel-law-favors-farmers-over-oil-giant-petrobras</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲两位富豪正在吸引印度家庭投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/asia-s-two-richest-men-are-wooing-india-s-mom-and-pop-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁穆克什·安巴尼 (Mukesh Ambani) 和高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 正在争取印度的散户投资者，因为这群人已经在印度金融市场站稳了脚跟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/asia-s-two-richest-men-are-wooing-india-s-mom-and-pop-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 11:43:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meloni 官员的目标是在两年内将意大利赤字降至 3% 以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/meloni-officials-aim-for-italy-deficit-below-3-within-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 领导的政府计划在未来两年内将意大利的赤字降至 3% 以下，以让正在审查意大利巨额债务的布鲁塞尔官员放心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/meloni-officials-aim-for-italy-deficit-below-3-within-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 11:12:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾伦·霍华德的儿子与同事创办了加密货币风险基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/alan-howard-s-son-starts-a-crypto-venture-fund-with-colleague</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国对冲基金亿万富翁艾伦·霍华德 (Alan Howard) 并不是家族中唯一的加密货币支持者。他的儿子丹尼尔·霍华德 (Daniel Howard) 和一位同事为一家专注于数字资产领域的新风险投资基金筹集了 2500 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/alan-howard-s-son-starts-a-crypto-venture-fund-with-colleague</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据公布前经济增长忧虑拖累欧洲股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/european-stocks-slip-as-growth-worries-weigh-ahead-of-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国经济衰退风险和中国经济增长放缓的担忧影响了本周晚些时候备受关注的就业报告出炉前的市场人气，欧洲股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/european-stocks-slip-as-growth-worries-weigh-ahead-of-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 07:18:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据公布后股市下跌，债券上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们权衡劳动力市场的好坏来寻找美联储下一步行动的线索，导致股市下跌，债市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
